<l>maṟṟiyā ṉeṉṉuḷēṉ maṉṉō avaroṭiyā </l>
<l> ṉuṟṟanā ḷuḷḷa vuḷēṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I live by remembering my (former) intercourse with him; if it were not so, how could I live ?</l>
